title: Stamford Studio Nice Neighborhood
posting_body: ['Lovely, small 250 sq ft studio apartment for rent in quiet Glenbrook neighborhood.', 'This unit provides excellent natural light, has a brand new wall mounted heating/cooling unit, and recently renovated.', 'Cable/internet will be tenants responsibility, all other utilities will be included in rent.', 'There is a small kitchen space with medium size fridge/freezer, microwave, and hot plate.', 'There is no full stove.', 'Plenty of street parking is available.', 'There is no laundry on site, there are multiple laundromats and laundry services nearby.', "2 months rent security deposit plus first month's rent will be due at signing.", 'Tenants will be responsible for holding renters insurance.', 'No pets, no smoking', 'Studio is ready for showing during final stage of renovation and will become available by August 14.', 'Please reply directly to this ad with any questions or interest in viewing the apartment']
